        <div class="lineline"></div>

        <h4>
            what are you planning to do next?
        </h4>
        <h2>
            i think im going to focus on me for a while, to feel more comfortable with myself but ill still be updating here, cause its fun
        </h2>

        <div class="lineline"></div>
        <h4>socials!</h4>
        <h2>
            <a href="">
                discord - roxcelic #0001
            </a>
        </h2>
